thread.title: Prosecutors seek 30 year jail term for South Korean ex-president

title: Prosecutors seek 30 year jail term for South Korean ex-president
text:
Prosecutors seek 30 year jail term for South Korean ex-president 10:37am GMT - 01:56 
South Korean prosecutors seek a 30-year jail term for former President Park Geun-hye who was ousted last year amid an influence-peddling scandal that rocked the country’s business and political elite. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
